<font color="#E8EBED">It doesn't work on you, does it?</font>

19
00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:57.640
<font color="#E8EBED">He was staring at you before, too.</font>

20
00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:01.000
<font color="#E8EBED">Hey, Ken.</font>

21
