<font color="#E8EBED">Good morning.</font>

23
00:01:04.660 --> 00:01:07.100
<font color="#E8EBED">I'm going back to work, \Nis that all right?</font>

24
00:01:07.100 --> 00:01:07.850
<font color="#E8EBED">Yes.</font>

25
00:01:07.850 --> 00:01:09.450
<font color="#E8EBED">Thank you.</font>

26
00:01:10.470 --> 00:01:11.470
<font color="#E8EBED">See you.</font>

27
00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:16.980
<font color="#E8EBED">Sorry to make you help me.</font>

28
00:01:17.420 --> 00:01:21.300
<font color="#E8EBED">Were you the one who induced the \NPauli effect on those glasses?</font>

29
00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:22.210
<font color="#E8EBED">Pau...?</font>

30
00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:24.180
<font color="#E8EBED">The Pauli effect.</font>

31
00:01:24.180 --> 00:01:29.520
<font color="#E8EBED">The theoretical physicist Wolfgang Pauli was \Nclumsy and often broke equipment.</font>

32
00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:34.770
<font color="#E8EBED">Apparently, he would sometimes break \Ntools just by touching or being near them.</font>

33
00:01:34.770 --> 00:01:38.260
<font color="#E8EBED">Because he broke things so often, \Nhis colleagues teased him,</font>

34
00:01:38.260 --> 00:01:41.330
<font color="#E8EBED">saying it was due to a mysterious power.</font>

35
00:01:41.330 --> 00:01:43.660
<font color="#E8EBED">That is the origin of the Pauli effect.</font>

36
00:01:43.660 --> 00:01:46.660
<font color="#E8EBED">In other words, you are clumsy like Pauli.</font>

37
00:01:46.660 --> 00:01:47.480
<font color="#E8EBED">That took forever!</font>

38
00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:50.120
<font color="#E8EBED">And way too indirect.</font>

39
00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:53.140
<font color="#E8EBED">Furthermore, working \Nwith an injured finger...</font>

40
00:01:53.140 --> 00:01:56.390
<font color="#E8EBED">can lead to a bacterial infection.</font>

41
00:01:56.390 --> 00:01:58.450
<font color="#E8EBED">Perhaps you should go home for today.</font>

42
00:01:58.910 --> 00:02:01.270
<font color="#E8EBED">That's...</font>

43
00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:03.880
<font color="#E8EBED">We'd like to keep looking, right?</font>

44
00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:05.960
<font color="#E8EBED">Make up a reason to stay.</font>

45
00:02:08.390 --> 00:02:11.970
<font color="#E8EBED">Um... Uh...</font>

46
00:02:13.300 --> 00:02:19.950
<font color="#E8EBED">It's really not a bad injury, \Nand I'd like to stay...</font>

47
00:02:19.950 --> 00:02:22.470
<font color="#E8EBED">Yeah, and I've had plenty of rest...</font>

48
00:02:22.470 --> 00:02:25.300
<font color="#E8EBED">But I'm still no good.</font>

49
00:02:25.300 --> 00:02:27.750
<font color="#E8EBED">I'd like to get more used to this... So...</font>

50
00:02:27.750 --> 00:02:30.430
<font color="#E8EBED">Um, I'm an inconvenience, aren't I?</font>

51
00:02:30.430 --> 00:02:32.230
<font color="#E8EBED">So I'll...</font>

52
00:02:32.230 --> 00:02:33.240
<font color="#E8EBED">Excuse me.</font>

53
00:02:33.700 --> 00:02:38.400
<font color="#E8EBED">Could you say what you're \Ntrying to say more logically?</font>

54
00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:43.950
<font color="#E8EBED">If I could, I'd rather not leave early.</font>

55
00:02:46.890 --> 00:02:48.830
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did I make him angry?</font>

56
00:02:50.440 --> 00:02:54.140
<font color="#E8EBED">His face is so inexpressive,\NI have no idea what he's thinking.</font>

57
00:02:54.140 --> 00:02:55.520
<font color="#E8EBED">Um... You see, I...</font>

58
00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.260
<font color="#E8EBED">I understand.</font>

59
00:02:56.770 --> 00:03:00.870
<font color="#E8EBED">You want to become more \Nused to your job, right?</font>

60
00:03:00.870 --> 00:03:03.770
<font color="#E8EBED">Then we will back you up.</font>

61
00:03:04.890 --> 00:03:07.740
<font color="#E8EBED">I'll explain the situation \Nto the manager.</font>

62
00:03:07.740 --> 00:03:09.840
<font color="#E8EBED">With that intuitive explanation of yours,</font>

63
00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:12.480
<font color="#E8EBED">I fear he won't understand.</font>

64
00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.280
<font color="#E8EBED">Please.</font>

65
00:03:15.810 --> 00:03:17.860
<font color="#E8EBED">Could he have been quiet because he...</font>

66
00:03:17.860 --> 00:03:21.300
<font color="#E8EBED">was trying to understand \Nwhat you were saying?</font>

67
00:03:22.540 --> 00:03:23.540
<font color="#E8EBED">I see.</font>

68
00:03:24.540 --> 00:03:26.170
<font color="#E8EBED">If that's the case...</font>

69
00:03:26.910 --> 00:03:29.400
<font color="#E8EBED">Thank you.</font>

70
00:03:30.880 --> 00:03:33.550
<font color="#E8EBED">Welcome back, milady.</font>

71
00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:47.140
<font color="#E8EBED">That was a close call, wasn't it?</font>

72
00:03:47.410 --> 00:03:49.480
